info.title: Registered Product
info.description: A registered product is an instance of a product that is associated with a specific customer and generally has a serial number. This service lists the header information of a registered product. Disclaimer: The list of entity type collections displayed under API References is not complete. To view the comprehensive list, see the service metadata.
